data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Assessments for city water & sewer Paid at Closing. Large Pool Home! Opportune location close to lots of shopping, restaurants & all the area amenities. This Big home boasts over 2250 sqft with a huge Florida room leading to solar heated pool & fenced dog run. Peace of mind with permanent Hurricane shutters all around, 2021 Roof, 2019 AC unit, 2015 Re-pipe, 2020 Pool resurfaced. Two living & dining areas making plenty of room for family & guests. Center of the home is the kitchen with a window to the Florida room & views of the pool. A Split bedroom floorplan offers privacy for everyone. Plenty of closet space in the main bedroom plus en-suite bathroom featuring dual sinks & a large, tiled shower. Two guest bedrooms that are quite large with walk in closets. The guest bath has a nicely tiled shower/tub combo & also serves the pool for convenience. Lots of possibilities in the Florida room, home office, gym, or playroom. Take a dip in the solar heated pool or end the evening in your private hot tub with a nice deck to lounge. Enjoy the shed to help store some garage items! Fresh paint inside and out! Assessments Paid - NO FLOOD ZONE!
